This diphthong begins with the AW as in LAW vowel.
这个双元音以 LAW 中的 AW 元音开始。

6
00:00:29,728 --> 00:00:31,260
As a part of the diphthong,
作为双元音的一部分，

7
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:36,060
