所以舌尖没有接触到任何东西。

12
00:00:49,340 --> 00:00:52,920
The ending position is the IH as in SIT vowel.
结束位置是 SIT 中的 IH 元音。

13
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:54,720
The lips relax,
嘴唇放松，

14
00:00:54,980 --> 00:00:56,480
and the tongue comes forward.
舌头向前移动。

15
00:00:56,940 --> 00:01:00,180
